did you spend your money on?

757
01:29:41,334 --> 01:29:46,046
I was never tired
of buying pianos, watches, radios.

758
01:29:46,130 --> 01:29:48,423
As long as they were foreign

759
01:29:48,508 --> 01:29:50,425
ofcourse.

760
01:29:50,510 --> 01:29:52,636
Anything western was good.

761
01:29:52,720 --> 01:29:56,932
